{
  "texts": [
    "These features encompassed gaze 2D data obtained from Pupil Invisible Glasses, joint Euler angles extracted from Perception Neuron Studio, EMG data collected from gForcePro + and Cognionics EMG sensors, as well as pressure and center of pressure data acquired from Moticon sensors.",
    "To synchronize these features, each sensor was integrated into the main computer's data collection framework.",
    "This involved fetching the Unix time and data from each sensor server and transmitting these simultaneously.",
    "Based on this approach, the Unix time and sensor data were collected simultaneously for five different sensors.",
    "We performed preprocessing for each sensor, and the preprocessing process is summarized in Fig. 12."
  ]
}